INSERT INTO `movie` VALUES ('40000000','',820,'en','JFK','New Orleans District Attorney Jim Garrison discovers there\'s more to the Kennedy assassination than the official story.','26',' Camelot Productions',' United States of America','1991-12-20','205405498','189','Released','The story that wont go away.','JFK','3.75','502','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjYyODExMDctZjgwYy00ZjQwLWI4OWYtOGFlYjA4ZjEzNmY1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTAyODkwOQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','400.00'),('3000000','',821,'en','Judgment at Nuremberg','In 1947, four German judges who served on the bench during the Nazi regime face a military tribunal to answer charges of crimes against humanity. Chief Justice Haywood hears evidence and testimony not only from lead defendant Ernst Janning and his defense attorney Hans Rolfe, but also from the widow of a Nazi general, an idealistic U.S. Army captain and reluctant witness Irene Wallner.','13',' United Artists',' Germany','1961-12-01','10000000','186','Released','The event the world will never forget','Judgment at Nuremberg','3.8','155','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDZjMTIwZTQtNTM3OS00OTUyLWI5MTMtOTNjYWVkNzhjMWIxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTc1NTQxODI@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','30.00'),('52500000','',824,'en','Moulin Rouge!','A celebration of love and creative inspiration takes place in the infamous, gaudy and glamorous Parisian nightclub, at the cusp of the 20th century. A young poet, who is plunged into the heady world of Moulin Rouge, begins a passionate affair with the club\'s most notorious and beautiful star.','57',' Bazmark Films',' Australia','2001-03-09','179213434','127','Released','No Laws. No Limits. One Rule. Never Fall In Love.','Moulin Rouge!','3.7','1300','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWFhYjliNjYtYjNhNS00OGExLWFhMjQtNDgwOWYyNWJiYzhmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTMxODk2OTU@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','525.00'),('3000000','',826,'en','The Bridge on the River Kwai','The classic story of English POWs in Burma forced to build a bridge to aid the war effort of their Japanese captors. British and American intelligence officers conspire to blow up the structure, but Col. Nicholson , the commander who supervised the bridge\'s construction, has acquired a sense of pride in his creation and tries to foil their plans.','23',' Columbia Pictures Corporation',' United Kingdom','1957-10-02','33300000','161','Released','It spans a whole new world of entertainment!','The Bridge on the River Kwai','3.85','542','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMGVhNjhjODktODgxYS00MDdhLTlkZjktYTkyNzQxMTU0ZDYxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','30.00'),('50000000','http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/underworldawakening/',834,'en','Underworld: Evolution','As the war between the vampires and the Lycans rages on, Selene, a former member of the Death Dealers (an elite vampire special forces unit that hunts werewolves), and Michael, the werewolf hybrid, work together in an effort to unlock the secrets of their respective bloodlines.','49',' Lakeshore Entertainment',' United States of America','2006-01-12','111340801','106','Released','My God. Brother, what have you done?','Underworld: Evolution','3.2','1528','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjEzNDY1OTQwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjcxMTIzMw@@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','500.00'),('5952000','',837,'en','Videodrome','A sleazy cable-TV programmer begins to see his life and the future of media spin out of control in a very unusual fashion when he acquires a new kind of programming for his station.','18',' Universal Pictures',' Canada','1983-02-04','2120439','87','Released','First it controls your mind. Then it destroys your body.','Videodrome','3.55','454','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzdlNDk0YTMtNWJjOS00NzhlLThiOTAtZDUyOWNkNDQ2NmU3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','59.52'),('40000000','',841,'en','Dune','In the year 10,191, the world is at war for control of the desert planet Dune  the only place where the time-travel substance \'Spice\' can be found. But when one leader gives up control, it\'s only so he can stage a coup with some unsavory characters.','25',' Dino De Laurentiis Company',' United States of America','1984-12-14','30925690','137','Released','A world beyond your experience, beyond your imagination.','Dune','3.25','562','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTAzYzNlMDMtMGRjYS00M2UxLTk0MmEtYmE4YWZiYmEwOTIwL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzc5MjA3OA@@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','400.00'),('12000000','http://www.wkw2046.com/',844,'zh','2046','2046 is the sequel to Wong Kar-Wais successful box-office hit In The Mood For Love. A film about affairs, ending relationships, and a shared love for Kung-Fu novels as the main character, Chow, writes his own novel and reflects back on his favorite love Su.','12',' Paradis Films',' Germany','2004-05-20','19271312','129','Released','Are you still in the mood for love?','2046','3.45','206','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzY1MjkzNDY4MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzE1NzAzMQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','120.00'),('66000000','',846,'en','The X Files','Mulder and Scully, now taken off the FBI\'s X Files cases, must find a way to fight the shadowy elements of the government to find out the truth about a conspiracy that might mean the alien colonization of Earth.','18',' Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation',' Canada','1998-06-19','189198313','121','Released','Fight the Future','The X Files','3.3','488','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDhkYTM1MmEtNTFhMC00NDEyLWI1MGQtMTkzMTcwMmM3ZTkzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDk3NzU2MTQ@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','660.00'),('18000000','',848,'en','Dragonslayer','The sorcerer and his apprentice Galen are on a mission to kill an evil dragon in order to save the Kings daughter from being sacrificed in accordance to a pact that the King himself made with the dragon to protect his kingdom. A fantasy film from Disney Studios that exhausted all possible visual effects of the time.','3',' Paramount Pictures',' United Kingdom','1981-06-26','14110013','108','Released','In the Dark Ages, Magic was a weapon. Love was a mystery. Adventure was everywhere... And Dragons were real.','Dragonslayer','3.25','67','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZmNhNjUxN2EtMTRkNi00YzAzLTg5ODgtZjc2ZTUyNDBjODljXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjExODE1MDc@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','180.00'),('27000000','',849,'en','Krull','A prince and a fellowship of companions set out to rescue his bride from a fortress of alien invaders who have arrived on their home planet.','9',' Columbia Pictures Corporation',' Spain','1983-07-29','16519460','117','Released','A world light-years beyond your imagination.','Krull','2.9','129','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDAwM2MyNmMtYTljMi00ZDJiLWJmOTktYjMzNGE3OGZiNTc2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTAyODkwOQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','270.00'),('68000000','',853,'en','Enemy at the Gates','Enemy at the Gates is a war film from Jean-Jacques Annaud from 2001 that takes place during the battle of Stalingard in World War II between the Russians and the Germans.','41',' Paramount Pictures',' Ireland','2001-03-13','96976270','131','Released','Some Men Are Born To Be Heroes.','Enemy at the Gates','3.6','999','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWFlY2E3ODQtZWNiNi00ZGU4LTkzNWEtZTQ2ZTViMWRhYjIzL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTAyODkwOQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg','0','680.00'),('23000000','',854,'en','The Mask','When timid bank clerk Stanley Ipkiss discovers a magical mask containing the spirit of the Norse god Loki, his entire life changes. While wearing the mask, Ipkiss becomes a supernatural playboy exuding charm and confidence which allows him to catch the eye of local nightclub singer Tina Carlyle. Unfortunately, under the mask\'s influence, Ipkiss also robs a bank, which angers junior crime lord Dorian Tyrell, whose goons get blamed for the heist.','85',' New Line Cinema',' United States of America','1994-07-29','351583407','101','Released','From zero to hero.','The Mask','3.3','2472','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWExYjI5MzktNTRhNi00Nzg2LThkZmQtYWVkYjRlYWI2MDQ4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTAyODkwOQ@@